1
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:15,680
Miss,

2
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,060
this flower

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,260
was destroyed by the Third Young Master.

4
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:24,690
If the Qionghua flower were alive,

5
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:26,960
Chu Shengyi would be able to control me.

6
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,240
He's not that stupid.

7
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:29,440
I was careless.

8
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:33,920
This flower,

9
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:36,540
when it was brought out from Qiwu Courtyard,

10
00:00:36,760 --> 00:00:38,560
its roots must have been burned.

11
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:40,500
Never mind.

12
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:43,250
He broke his promise first,

13
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,500
and I destroyed the painting.

14
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:46,600
We are even.

15
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:49,040
Speaking of this.

16
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:55,760
Right, Miss.

17
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:57,320
Didn't you ask me to keep an eye on

18
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,960
the information trade in Wuming Workshop?

19
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,220
I found out something.

20
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:03,080
Take a look at this, Miss.

21
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,760
The traveling merchant from the Western Regions

22
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,080
is said to appear in the black market tonight.

23
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,960
Rumor has it that the merchant has

24
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,600
the Qionghua seeds.

25
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,200
Really?

26
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,000
Qionghua seeds are rare.

27
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,480
I have been looking for them for years to no avail.

28
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,800
But to buy things from the traveling merchant

29
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,280
is not an easy task.

30
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,370
That merchant has weird rules.

31
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,800
One must first solve the puzzle

32
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,730
to get the token.

33
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,800
To get the token now,

34
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,240
it must be too late.

35
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,009
I can't care so much now.

36
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,640
The Qionghua flower is destroyed.

37
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,770
The Qionghua seeds,

38
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,500
I must get my hands on them.

39
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,120
Granny,

40
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,160
stay here.

41
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,640
In case something happens,

42
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,640
we would all be trapped in the black market

43
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,840
and unable to escape.

44
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,600
But without the token,

45
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:48,259
how can you make the merchant give you the seeds?

46
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,960
We can only play it by ear.

47
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,920
This traveling merchant's temperament is really weird.

48
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,240
I heard there is another test.

49
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,440
Do you know what it is?

50
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,640
Nobody knows.

51
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:22,920
Even Wuming Workshop

52
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,450
can't buy any information.

53
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,250
Could this be the token?

54
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,079
Knife wound.

55
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,320
Are you blind?

56
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,880
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

57
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,600
No, this is the dendrobium I just picked.

58
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:46,329
I was going to sell it in the black market for rice.

59
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,760
The grain in our Kuizhou

60
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,400
can make a dog wag its tail

61
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,520
and make a pig grow some meat.

62
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:56,160
Feeding you, a lowly skinny thing,

63
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,320
is simply a waste.

64
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,160
A waste.

65
00:02:59,240 --> 00:02:59,880
Stop it.

66
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,280
The black market is not regulated by Kuizhou laws.

67
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,360
Only business matters here,

68
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,290
not your origin.

69
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,000
You

70
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,920
shouldn't treat her like this.

71
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:10,120
Another piece of bad luck.

72
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,400
It's not your turn to teach me a lesson.

73
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,800
Are you asking for death?

74
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:19,640
You...

75
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,610
Who do you think you are?

76
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,079
Mind your own business.

77
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,240
You're blocking my way.

78
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,560
Do you own the road?

79
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,370
Do you know who my father is?

80
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,490
Apologize to this lady.

81
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,320
Why?

82
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:32,960
Because

83
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,090
if you hurt someone,

84
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,660
you should apologize.

85
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,040
I only hurt a thin slave.

86
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,040
What does fat or thin,

87
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,840
rich or poor,

88
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:40,880
have to do with it?

89
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,860
You are facing a person right now.

90
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,660
Apologize.

91
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,079
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

92
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,760
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

93
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,240
Sorry.

94
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,280
Get out.

95
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:01,770
Sword wound.

96
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:05,080
Could it be related to the wandering merchant too?

97
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:11,020
There's actually someone in Kuizhou who doesn't despise thin women.

98
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,240
Why are you following me?

99
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:46,080
I just offended that fat man.

100
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,720
Seeing that you have great skills,

101
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,520
it must be safer to follow you.

102
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,050
My family is strict.

103
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,960
I sneaked out today

104
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,680
just to see the novelties in the black market.

105
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,240
I promise

106
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,570
I won't disturb your business.

107
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:04,320
No.

108
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,540
This copper rouge box is a rarity.

109
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,680
In the whole Kuizhou City,

110
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,410
you can't find another one now.

111
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,840
Take a close look.

112
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,480
I want this. Name your price.

113
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,740
What a joke. This brass rouge box is rare.

114
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:23,010
I'm missing this one in my collection.

115
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,690
Name your price.

116
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,100
Don't move.

117
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,600
Hand it over,

118
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,200
or her life is forfeit.

119
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:34,680
Whatever.

120
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,680
Sir,

121
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,560
it's useless to hold me hostage.

122
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,000
We really don't know each other.

123
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,400
Stop pretending, you two.

124
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,640
If you didn't know each other,

125
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,960
would you have protected her so much

126
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,800
at the entrance of the black market just now?

127
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,440
Wait.

128
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:53,080
This copper rouge box with the official seal of Linlang Pavilion,

129
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,760
only ten of them were made back then.

130
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:57,240
It is a specially made antique replica by the officials.

131
00:05:57,240 --> 00:06:00,040
Later, a batch of affordable improved versions were copied

132
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,240
and are still in use today.

133
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,720
Why not take it under the light

134
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,580
and take a look?

135
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,480
This copper rouge box

136
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,680
is not brass at all,

137
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,840
but made of gold-plated bronze.

138
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,800
Since you said

139
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,680
you've collected rouge boxes for years

140
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,210
and seen countless of them,

141
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,240
how come you can't even tell it's bronze

142
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,680
instead of brass?

143
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,520
Since it's a fake,

144
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,010
then I don't want it.

145
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,040
Let's go.

146
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,960
I heard Qionghua doesn't exist in the Western Regions anymore.

147
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:52,800
Really?

148
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,320
It's absolutely true.

149
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,580
I just came from there.

150
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,760
Even if there were,

151
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,820
they couldn't survive the long journey now.

152
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,420
You don't still plan to do this business, do you?

153
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,520
Who made our Madam Li

154
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,480
like it?

155
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,040
But then again,

156
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,960
this flower is really weird.

157
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,280
It has no stamens,

158
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,810
no seeds, and no fruits.

159
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,840
Where the seeds come from

160
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,440
remains unknown to this day.

161
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,760
It's something you can only hope for, not seek.

162
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:21,680
I also heard

163
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,560
the Qionghua in Madam Li's private garden

164
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,600
were all burned down a few days ago.

165
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,320
Yes, what a pity.

166
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,560
In that case,

167
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:31,640
this might be the last seed in the world.

168
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,260
It must be very expensive.

169
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,000
Sorry, everyone.

170
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,360
I know why you are here tonight,

171
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,960
but tonight,

172
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,000
my goods

173
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,159
will only be sold to these two.

174
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,080
- Why?
- Why?

175
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,900
- Why?
- Why?

176
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,840
Because my goods are unique in the world.

177
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:53,890
If you still want to do business with me in the future,

178
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,450
you have to follow my rules.

179
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,400
Please. This is outrageous.

180
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,280
Stop!

181
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,120
It's you.

182
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,080
So at the entrance just now,

183
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,720
was that also your way of picking customers?

184
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,160
In Kuizhou, fat is considered precious,

185
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,970
so I insist on defining business by thinness.

186
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,680
Qionghua is unique in the world.

187
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,120
I won't sell it to those

188
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,280
prejudiced

189
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,600
fools.

190
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,360
Come on.

191
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,380
Where's the token?

192
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,039
I want to see your sincerity.

193
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,080
What about yours?

194
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,640
Can I borrow your knife, Sir?

195
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:56,640
Knife?

196
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:09,720
I saw that all the merchants just now had knife wounds on their hands.

197
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,760
I guess showing sincerity requires some blood.

198
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:14,490
I wonder if this counts as passing the first test.

199
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,320
Brilliant.

200
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,040
You are so interesting.

201
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,560
Since you are so sincere,

202
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,280
I'll break

203
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,880
the rule tonight.

204
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,640
It's a pity.

205
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,520
There is only one

206
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,440
Qionghua seed.

207
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:41,920
Why don't

208
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:45,080
we play a game of uncovering the veil?

209
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,560
Uncovering the veil?

210
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,720
There is a children's game in the Western Regions called uncovering the veil.

211
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,800
Within the time it takes for a stick of incense to burn,

212
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:53,400
the one who reveals the other's true face wins.

213
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,920
The winner gets the Qionghua seed.

214
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:02,800
Wait a minute.

215
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,320
This gentleman is highly skilled,

216
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,850
while I am just a weak woman.

217
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,130
It's not fair to compete like this.

218
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,290
Makes sense.

219
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,000
In that case,

220
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:15,840
since it's a children's game,

221
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,980
let's play it the children's way.

222
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,960
We won't use martial arts.

223
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,520
Also,

224
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,080
within half an incense stick of time,

225
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:24,600
if you fail to take off the lady's mask,

226
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,120
the lady wins.

227
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,050
How about it?

228
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,920
Deal.

229
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:32,800
Alright.

230
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,520
Let's begin.

231
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,920
It's him.

232
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,720
His legs are indeed fine.

233
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,960
The rule of the black market

234
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,440
is to exchange secrets for something of equal value.

235
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,560
Since you could leave your crutch

236
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,280
at home so easily,

237
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,760
why don't you offer me something

238
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,080
to keep my mouth shut?

239
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,720
The black market is full of all sorts of people.

240
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,320
If I call out your name loudly

241
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,080
and let everyone know

242
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,480
that you came to the black market with your legs intact

243
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,940
to get the Qionghua seeds,

244
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,760
guess what Mother will do

245
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,840
tomorrow?

246
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:19,540
I can spare your life, my lady.

247
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,800
But my lady,

248
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,460
you must protect this secret with your life.

249
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,240
Otherwise...

250
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,340
Thank you, my lady.

251
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:39,600
The Qionghua seed is mine.

